Faq.QuestionTwo: Do I need anything special to use it?
Faq.descriptionOne: Resume of the future. For 20+ years we have been using PDF for resume, it is time to move forward to the new age of mobile responsive, sharable, passcode protected
Faq.descriptionTwo: All you need to use LeetCV is an internet connection or a mobile phone. Join us here! Once you're in, begin finding and following accounts whose resumes interest you. We'll recommend great accounts once you're signed up.
